1
00:00:08,987 --> 00:00:09,715
<i>C'mon!</i>

2
00:00:16,361 --> 00:00:18,852
<i>Running like a fugitive,</i>

3
00:00:19,998 --> 00:00:22,057
<i>Being chased by something</i>

4
00:00:23,735 --> 00:00:26,397
<i>Inside my heart is pounding</i>

5
00:00:27,739 --> 00:00:30,367
<i>My throat dry like it's withering</i>

6
00:00:32,010 --> 00:00:35,104
<i>For no single one,</i>

7
00:00:35,781 --> 00:00:38,841
<i>To none does belong,</i>

8
00:00:40,185 --> 00:00:44,451
<i>This time is ours, right now...</i>

9
00:00:47,225 --> 00:00:49,090
<i>Unraveling the pain,</i>

10
00:00:49,194 --> 00:00:50,923
<i>Unraveling our hearts,</i>

11
00:00:50,996 --> 00:00:53,328
<i>Unraveling shadows</i>

12
00:00:54,866 --> 00:00:56,629
<i>Stifling our breath,</i>

13
00:00:56,701 --> 00:00:58,601
<i>Reaching for beyond,</i>

14
00:00:58,670 --> 00:01:01,104
<i>Tearing through the dark</i>

15
00:01:03,008 --> 00:01:09,572
<i>In fighting and in love</i>

16
00:01:10,549 --> 00:01:13,177
<i>To the distant light above,</i>

17
00:01:13,852 --> 00:01:16,821
<i>Yes, we are on the way</i>

18
00:01:21,626 --> 00:01:22,854
<i>I wanna rock...</i>

19
00:01:25,430 --> 00:01:26,954
<i>Rockin' my heart</i>

20
00:01:55,221 --> 00:01:56,518
<i>Such intensity...</i>

21
00:01:58,057 --> 00:02:03,256
<i>If I take a breath or move my eyes</i>
<i>I will be marked and killed</i> -

22
00:02:03,663 --> 00:02:04,789
<i>that's what I'm feeling...</i>

23
00:02:05,865 --> 00:02:09,801
<i>If I'm stuck like this for an hour,</i>
<i>I'll go mad.</i>

24
00:02:11,437 --> 00:02:13,530
<i>Facing a Jonin intent to kill...</i>

25
00:02:14,607 --> 00:02:17,667
<i>This sensation is like having</i>
<i>my life held in limbo...</i>

26
00:02:20,079 --> 00:02:24,243
<i>No way! I'd rather die</i>
<i>to escape this feeling!</i>

27
00:02:26,018 --> 00:02:26,780
Sasuke...

28
00:02:27,687 --> 00:02:31,589
Don't worry. I'll protect
you all with my life.

29
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:38,187
I absolutely won't allow
my comrades to get killed.

30
00:02:43,469 --> 00:02:45,528
I don't know about that...

31
00:02:52,612 --> 00:02:53,544
It's over.

32
00:03:24,543 --> 00:03:25,771
Sensei! Behind you!!

33
00:03:30,816 --> 00:03:32,215
Die!!

34
00:03:43,829 --> 00:03:45,421
<i>The Water Clone Jutsu...?</i>

35
00:03:47,066 --> 00:03:47,828
<i>It can't be.</i>

36
00:03:52,538 --> 00:03:53,300
Don't move!

37
00:04:00,012 --> 00:04:05,973
<i>The Oath of Pain</i>

38
00:04:17,797 --> 00:04:18,661
It's over.

39
00:04:21,367 --> 00:04:22,561
W-Wow!!

40
00:04:33,813 --> 00:04:35,178
Did you say it's over?

41
00:04:36,849 --> 00:04:38,714
You don't understand, do you?

42
00:04:39,819 --> 00:04:43,619
You won't be able to beat me
just by making like a monkey...

43
00:04:44,457 --> 00:04:45,651
No chance.

44
00:04:51,363 --> 00:04:53,228
But, I must say you're good.

45
00:04:54,100 --> 00:04:59,868
My Water Clone Jutsu was
being copied at that point...

46
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:04,640
<i>I absolutely won't allow</i>
<i>my comrades to get killed.</i>

47
00:05:05,978 --> 00:05:13,714
By letting the clone talk as if it were you,
you succeeded in distracting me.

48
00:05:14,487 --> 00:05:20,585
And you used Hidden Mist Jutsu
to hide yourself to see what I was doing...

49
00:05:23,162 --> 00:05:24,254
But...

50
00:05:25,631 --> 00:05:27,792
I'm not a fool.

51
00:05:30,002 --> 00:05:31,492
That one was a fake too!

52
00:05:46,418 --> 00:05:47,077
<i>Now!</i>

53
00:05:51,524 --> 00:05:52,422
<i>Makibishi spikes!</i>

54
00:05:56,328 --> 00:05:57,386
How foolish!

55
00:05:59,965 --> 00:06:00,761
Sensei!

56
00:06:01,500 --> 00:06:03,991
<i>Oh, I can't believe that</i>
<i>Kakashi Sensei got...</i>

57
00:06:05,004 --> 00:06:06,062
<i>kicked away like that...</i>

58
00:06:07,807 --> 00:06:10,071
His Taijutsu skills are also
extremely good.

59
00:06:14,747 --> 00:06:18,342
<i>W-What's with this water...?</i>
<i>It's awfully heavy.</i>

60
00:06:18,984 --> 00:06:20,713
Humph... Fool!

61
00:06:21,654 --> 00:06:22,916
It's the Water Prison Jutsu!

62
00:06:23,622 --> 00:06:24,213
<i>Darn it.</i>

63
00:06:27,226 --> 00:06:29,353
<i>My temporary escape</i>
<i>into the water...</i>

64
00:06:29,428 --> 00:06:30,417
<i>was a huge mistake!</i>

65
00:06:33,666 --> 00:06:34,758
You're caught...

66
00:06:35,134 --> 00:06:37,625
It's a special prison that makes
it impossible for you to escape!

67
00:06:38,838 --> 00:06:41,363
It makes things harder
having you able to act.

68
00:06:42,875 --> 00:06:44,342
Now... Kakashi.

69
00:06:45,110 --> 00:06:47,340
I'll have to settle things
with you later.

70
00:06:48,113 --> 00:06:51,605
First, I will finish those guys off.

71
00:06:52,685 --> 00:06:54,152
Water Clone Jutsu...

72
00:06:55,654 --> 00:06:57,121
<i>Didn't expect this level of skill...</i>

73
00:07:09,501 --> 00:07:12,834
You're acting big,
wearing a headband like a Ninja...

74
00:07:13,639 --> 00:07:17,268
But... a real Ninja is one

75
00:07:17,743 --> 00:07:21,042
who has hovered between
life and death numerous times.

76
00:07:22,047 --> 00:07:22,979
In other words,

77
00:07:23,449 --> 00:07:26,384
only those who are worth being listed
in my Bingo Book

78
00:07:26,452 --> 00:07:28,579
deserve to be called Ninja.

79
00:07:30,289 --> 00:07:34,658
Guys like you can't be
called real Ninja.

80
00:07:35,761 --> 00:07:36,728
<i>He's disappeared again!</i>

81
00:07:47,139 --> 00:07:48,663
You're just a kid!

82
00:07:49,942 --> 00:07:50,601
Naruto!

83
00:07:53,412 --> 00:07:56,506
You three! Take Tazuna and run!

84
00:07:56,949 --> 00:07:58,382
You have no chance
against this guy!

85
00:07:59,118 --> 00:08:01,518
As long as he has me trapped
in this Water Prison,

86
00:08:01,587 --> 00:08:03,020
he won't be able
to move from here.

87
00:08:03,522 --> 00:08:05,217
And he shouldn't be able to use
the Water Clone Jutsu

88
00:08:05,291 --> 00:08:07,452
if he's far enough away
from his real body.

89
00:08:08,060 --> 00:08:09,584
In any case, just run for now!

90
00:08:10,696 --> 00:08:11,924
<i>Run away?</i>

91
00:08:12,498 --> 00:08:13,863
<i>You've got to be kidding me.</i>

92
00:08:14,667 --> 00:08:18,364
<i>That option was gone</i>
<i>from the moment you got caught.</i>

93
00:08:19,371 --> 00:08:20,895
<i>Even if we ran,</i>

94
00:08:20,973 --> 00:08:24,568
<i>without you, sooner or later</i>
<i>we'd be defeated by Zabuza...</i>

95
00:08:25,444 --> 00:08:26,411
<i>and we'd all be destroyed.</i>

96
00:08:28,213 --> 00:08:30,511
<i>Even if we were to reform</i>
<i>the Manji defense,</i>

97
00:08:30,683 --> 00:08:33,049
<i>it would be impossible</i>
<i>to block his attacks.</i>

98
00:08:34,386 --> 00:08:35,353
<i>In the end...</i>

99
00:08:35,888 --> 00:08:37,219
<i>we'll have...</i>

100
00:08:37,890 --> 00:08:39,187
<i>no options left.</i>

101
00:08:39,858 --> 00:08:44,591
<i>In order for us to survive,</i>
<i>our only option is to rescue you.</i>

102
00:08:45,464 --> 00:08:46,692
We'll just have to do it!

103
00:09:01,613 --> 00:09:02,875
There!

104
00:09:03,015 --> 00:09:03,811
Too easy.

105
00:09:12,591 --> 00:09:13,455
Sasuke!

106
00:09:14,560 --> 00:09:15,549
Sasuke...

107
00:09:19,465 --> 00:09:23,765
<i>T-This is the Jonin level...</i>
<i>A real Ninja...</i>

108
00:09:24,303 --> 00:09:26,828
<i>We've got to run...</i>
<i>At this rate...</i>

109
00:09:27,773 --> 00:09:30,264
<i>Seriously! Seriously!</i>

110
00:09:30,476 --> 00:09:31,374
<i>We'll be killed!!</i>

111
00:09:50,362 --> 00:09:53,593
I'm going to swear on
the pain of my left hand!

112
00:09:55,667 --> 00:10:00,036
I'll never get into another situation
from which I'll have to be rescued...

113
00:10:01,673 --> 00:10:04,608
I'll never be afraid or
be a coward.

114
00:10:05,711 --> 00:10:09,909
Are you hurt... scaredy cat?

115
00:10:11,150 --> 00:10:13,175
<i>I won't lose to Sasuke.</i>

116
00:10:24,930 --> 00:10:28,388
Can I borrow that
Leaf headband for a while?

117
00:10:29,435 --> 00:10:29,992
This?

118
00:10:30,569 --> 00:10:36,303
This is worn only by those who have
graduated from Ninja Academy.

119
00:10:37,376 --> 00:10:41,938
Naruto, come over here.
I'd like to give you something.

120
00:10:43,949 --> 00:10:46,645
Congratulations on your graduation.

121
00:10:47,619 --> 00:10:49,109
That's because you're
all squirts

122
00:10:49,188 --> 00:10:51,918
who don't have the qualifications
to become Ninjas.

123
00:10:53,759 --> 00:10:56,353
Missions are all risky assignments.

124
00:10:58,597 --> 00:10:59,723
You pass!

125
00:11:00,132 --> 00:11:05,661
I'm not that little prankster
that you think I am!

126
00:11:06,839 --> 00:11:08,101
I'm going to surpass the Hokage!

127
00:11:08,907 --> 00:11:11,569
And so I'm going to get
the entire Village

128
00:11:11,643 --> 00:11:13,907
to acknowledge my existence!

129
00:11:15,547 --> 00:11:16,206
<i>That's right...</i>

130
00:11:16,682 --> 00:11:20,209
<i>I am a Ninja now. And...</i>

131
00:11:21,286 --> 00:11:23,880
<i>I decided that I was not going</i>
<i>to run anymore!</i>

132
00:11:25,124 --> 00:11:26,216
<i>That I wouldn't run away!</i>

133
00:11:31,430 --> 00:11:32,829
Y-You fool! Stop it!

134
00:11:33,232 --> 00:11:36,895
Oh, Naruto! What are you thinking?!

135
00:11:37,803 --> 00:11:40,101
Humph! Fool...

136
00:11:54,453 --> 00:11:57,047
What are you thinking...
charging off on your own?!

137
00:11:57,389 --> 00:11:59,016
Even Sasuke is no match for him...

138
00:11:59,458 --> 00:12:03,485
No matter how hard we try,
we Genin are no match for him...

139
00:12:10,569 --> 00:12:11,228
Huh?!

140
00:12:18,644 --> 00:12:19,542
<i>The headband...?!</i>

141
00:12:36,962 --> 00:12:39,556
Hey! You, with no brows...

142
00:12:41,867 --> 00:12:45,325
Record in your Bingo Book...

143
00:12:45,404 --> 00:12:48,999
about the man who will one day
become the Leaf Village's Hokage.

144
00:12:55,981 --> 00:12:57,846
Leaf-style Ninja...

145
00:12:59,151 --> 00:13:01,449
Naruto Uzumaki!!

146
00:13:05,724 --> 00:13:06,418
Naruto...

147
00:13:07,793 --> 00:13:13,231
<i>When I first saw that little kid,</i>
<i>he seemed so unreliable...</i>

148
00:13:13,799 --> 00:13:16,563
Sasuke! Lend me your ear!

149
00:13:16,702 --> 00:13:17,430
What is it?

150
00:13:17,903 --> 00:13:19,131
I have a plan.

151
00:13:20,806 --> 00:13:23,104
<i>You want to discuss plans</i>
<i>under these circumstances?</i>

152
00:13:23,609 --> 00:13:24,337
<i>This guy!</i>

153
00:13:25,677 --> 00:13:28,669
Humph!
You are talking of teamwork?

154
00:13:29,648 --> 00:13:32,481
<i>W-What is this feeling?</i>

155
00:13:33,585 --> 00:13:35,109
<i>Was Naruto so?</i>

156
00:13:36,622 --> 00:13:37,611
Now...

157
00:13:38,924 --> 00:13:40,289
Let's get wild...

158
00:14:14,661 --> 00:14:17,892
Now, let's get wild!

159
00:14:22,268 --> 00:14:25,704
Such loud snorting,
but do you have a winning plan?

160
00:14:26,539 --> 00:14:28,336
<i>T-This isn't good...</i>

161
00:14:28,675 --> 00:14:31,269
What are you guys doing!
I told you to run!

162
00:14:31,778 --> 00:14:33,973
It was obvious what was going to happen
once I was caught!

163
00:14:34,280 --> 00:14:35,042
Hurny! Run!

164
00:14:35,748 --> 00:14:39,081
Listen to me!
Our mission is to protect Tazuna!

165
00:14:39,752 --> 00:14:40,980
Have you forgotten that?!

166
00:14:45,091 --> 00:14:45,955
Old man...

167
00:14:50,330 --> 00:14:51,422
Well...

168
00:14:52,565 --> 00:14:54,999
This is a seed that I planted...

169
00:14:55,335 --> 00:14:58,862
I can't say that
I want my life to be spared.

170
00:15:00,139 --> 00:15:02,164
Sorry, you guys...

171
00:15:02,742 --> 00:15:04,676
Fight as much as you want!

172
00:15:06,679 --> 00:15:07,737
You hear that?

173
00:15:09,082 --> 00:15:10,447
Are you ready?

174
00:15:20,760 --> 00:15:22,921
You guys really haven't learned
anything, have you?

175
00:15:23,363 --> 00:15:24,796
W-What?!

176
00:15:25,798 --> 00:15:28,028
You're still playing at being Ninja?

177
00:15:28,534 --> 00:15:31,935
When I was your age,

178
00:15:32,639 --> 00:15:35,767
this hand was already
stained red with blood!

179
00:15:38,278 --> 00:15:39,939
Zabuza, the Demon!

180
00:15:40,546 --> 00:15:44,676
Ohh? It seems that
you've heard of me.

181
00:15:47,487 --> 00:15:52,151
A long time ago, in the Mist Village,
often called the town of Blood Mist,

182
00:15:52,992 --> 00:15:55,859
Ninja candidates faced
their biggest hurdle.

183
00:15:58,831 --> 00:16:01,595
So you also know about
that graduation exam...

184
00:16:02,335 --> 00:16:04,098
That graduation exam?

185
00:16:06,572 --> 00:16:08,267
What is it?

186
00:16:08,508 --> 00:16:10,373
This graduation exam
that you're talking about...

187
00:16:16,382 --> 00:16:18,680
The students killed each other.

188
00:16:19,085 --> 00:16:19,710
What?

189
00:16:25,058 --> 00:16:28,084
Classmates who had shared rice
from the same pot

190
00:16:28,227 --> 00:16:30,491
formed pairs and tried
to kill each other.

191
00:16:30,997 --> 00:16:33,591
It didn't end
until one of them died.

192
00:16:34,534 --> 00:16:40,473
Partners who used to talk about
each other's dreams and aspirations...

193
00:16:43,009 --> 00:16:43,839
How cruel...

194
00:16:45,511 --> 00:16:46,739
Ten years ago,

195
00:16:47,013 --> 00:16:51,609
the Mist Village's graduation exam
was forced to undergo drastic reform.

196
00:16:52,952 --> 00:16:58,185
That was because an evil demon
had appeared on the scene the previous year.

197
00:17:03,863 --> 00:17:04,830
Reform?

198
00:17:08,835 --> 00:17:09,995
What about the reform?

199
00:17:10,536 --> 00:17:12,970
What had that evil demon done?

200
00:17:14,407 --> 00:17:17,740
With no scruples or hesitation...

201
00:17:18,778 --> 00:17:21,838
a young boy who didn't even have
the qualifications for being a Ninja,

202
00:17:22,315 --> 00:17:27,218
annihilated over a hundred examinees.

203
00:17:37,630 --> 00:17:41,396
That sure was... fun...

204
00:17:55,181 --> 00:17:56,079
Sasuke!

205
00:18:15,034 --> 00:18:15,966
Die!

206
00:18:18,438 --> 00:18:19,666
Darn!

207
00:18:20,273 --> 00:18:21,865
Shadow Clone Jutsu!

208
00:18:25,812 --> 00:18:30,875
Ah... Shadow Clone Jutsu,
and there are quite a few of them.

209
00:18:54,240 --> 00:18:55,639
Here I go!

210
00:19:14,961 --> 00:19:16,895
It's impossible, after all...

211
00:19:17,363 --> 00:19:19,729
There is no way that
you can defeat the guy!

212
00:19:23,836 --> 00:19:26,999
<i>There is only one way left</i>
<i>to defeat this guy!</i>

213
00:19:27,840 --> 00:19:28,568
Sasuke!

214
00:19:33,279 --> 00:19:33,870
<i>I see!</i>

215
00:19:34,080 --> 00:19:36,048
<i>So that's your plan, Naruto!</i>

216
00:19:36,215 --> 00:19:37,807
<i>That's pretty good for you!</i>

217
00:19:52,999 --> 00:19:54,296
Demon Wind Shuriken,

218
00:19:54,734 --> 00:19:55,826
Windmill of Shadows...

219
00:20:04,977 --> 00:20:07,878
A Shuriken won't work on me.

220
00:20:22,962 --> 00:20:27,899
I see. This time
it's aiming for my real body...

221
00:20:29,001 --> 00:20:29,592
But...

222
00:20:30,303 --> 00:20:31,133
It's not so easy!

223
00:20:34,941 --> 00:20:37,307
A Shuriken in
the Shuriken's shadow!

224
00:20:37,610 --> 00:20:40,602
<i>This is...</i>
<i>The Shadow Shuriken Jutsu!</i>

225
00:20:41,847 --> 00:20:44,008
<i>A second Shuriken</i>
<i>in his blind spot!</i>

226
00:20:54,360 --> 00:20:54,985
But...

227
00:20:56,829 --> 00:20:58,558
Still too naïve...

228
00:21:00,099 --> 00:21:01,123
<i>He dodged it!!</i>

229
00:21:14,313 --> 00:21:16,178
Here it is!

230
00:22:52,280 --> 00:22:54,407
Yes! The plan worked!!

231
00:22:54,682 --> 00:22:58,345
That Zabuza had no clue
as to what I was thinking,

232
00:22:58,519 --> 00:23:00,749
and I fooled him!

233
00:23:01,556 --> 00:23:03,649
Ninja must be able
to see through the obvious.

234
00:23:03,891 --> 00:23:07,622
Did you see that - the Leaf style fighting
of Naruto Uzumaki?!

235
00:23:07,895 --> 00:23:10,295
Kakashi Sensei,
the rest is up to you.

236
00:23:11,232 --> 00:23:13,530
Next episode:
"Kakashi, Sharingan Warrior!"

237
00:23:13,668 --> 00:23:16,501
I'm going to kick butt once again!
